reviewText: I loved this show when it was on.  Very happy to be able to buy it now on dvd.  I am enjoying seeing it again
Absolutely Love the Series and Excellent reproduction of the original Tapes.

You know, I seemed to remember these shows being at the very least interesting? Well, I can tell you they aren't. Except of the original movie with David Duchovny and Billy Wirth...the rest are simply dull and not worth anyone's time.
